description:
Benny Gold is proud to let you know that their collection has expanded to include denim. It took half a year of sampling and multiple revisions to get it done just right. The denim is made in the USA of high quality materials available in a raw indigo, murdered out black, washed grey or raw indigo selvage.

It's not too baggy and not too slim. The fit is perfect and still gives you leg room to run from the cops or jump on the board and bike.

Here are a few examples of the many details put into our denim:

Classic designed hand burned leather tags
Sectioned off pen holder in the coin pocket, gold buttons and waist band print
Paper plane flight pattern back pocket arcuate

We recommend you order 1 size down to start

100% Cotton Denim
